	•	Realtor (Partner) → confidence, speed, reliability

⸻

🧱 SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE

1. 📁 CLIENT MISSION FOLDER (1 THREAD PER BORROWER)

Each borrower gets:

🔹 A. Snapshot
	•	Name
	•	Scenario (purchase/refi)
	•	Loan type
	•	Price / loan amount
	•	Timeline
	•	Referral source

🔹 B. Current Stage
	•	Pre-Approval
	•	Shopping
	•	Under Contract
	•	Processing
	•	Underwriting
	•	CTC
	•	Closing

🔹 C. Known Facts
	•	Income
	•	Assets
	•	Credit
	•	Employment
	•	Property details

🔹 D. Missing Items
	•	Docs needed
	•	Conditions
	•	Verifications pending

🔹 E. Risk Board ⚠️
	•	DTI tight
	•	Large deposits
	•	Credit fluctuation
	•	Appraisal risk
	•	Job changes

🔹 F. Next 3 Actions (MANDATORY)
	•	Always defined
	•	Always updated

🔹 G. Communication Log
	•	Date / interaction / promise made

🔹 H. Drafts
	•	Texts
	•	Emails
	•	Call scripts

