2. 🎯 PIPELINE ENGINE (3 VIEWS)

Same loan. Three realities.

⸻

🔷 PIPELINE 1: INTERNAL (OPERATOR VIEW)

🧠 Purpose:

Full situational awareness. No surprises.

LOAN PIPELINE — OPERATOR VIEW

[1] Pre-Approval
→ Pull credit, run AUS, issue letter

[2] Shopping
→ Monitor changes, update scenarios

[3] Under Contract
→ Collect contract, lock strategy

[4] Processing
→ Docs in, disclosures, appraisal ordered

[5] Underwriting
→ Submit file, clear conditions

[6] Clear to Close
→ Final CD, closing prep

[7] Closing
→ Fund + confirm

----------------------------

⚠️ RISKS:
- Large deposit: $8,500 (needs sourcing)
- DTI: borderline at 47%

📂 MISSING:
- 2nd bank statement
- VOE pending

🎯 NEXT 3 ACTIONS:
1. Get LOE for deposit
2. Submit updated docs
3. Prep for UW conditions


